content: 'The Eurocrypt conference is an international conference on all aspects of cryptology. The Eurocrypt conference has been held every year since 1987, and is held in a different location in Europe every year. For information about organizing Eurocrypt in the future, contact an Officer or a Director in the Board of Directors.
